1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,890
[Episode 59]

2
00:00:02,890 --> 00:00:06,810
Desperately trying to
become someone beautiful

3
00:00:06,810 --> 00:00:09,250
To redeem myself
in that terrible relationship

4
00:00:09,250 --> 00:00:12,810
And those cruel words spoken
because of someone's misunderstanding

5
00:00:12,810 --> 00:00:15,970
Only to end up being called a slut

6
00:00:15,970 --> 00:00:19,050
The deep scars left
by my first love

7
00:00:19,050 --> 00:00:21,870
Destroyed everything
that should have been beautiful

8
00:00:21,870 --> 00:00:25,270
And now I'm standing here
like a fool

9
00:00:25,340 --> 00:00:28,990
Still asking who should be responsible
for everything I've lost

10
00:00:44,070 --> 00:00:47,670
Fuzhi got a scholarship
to study animation in Japan

11
00:00:47,870 --> 00:00:51,950
Before leaving, he said
he was sorry for everything

12
00:00:52,390 --> 00:00:54,250
Then why didn't he
call me himself

13
00:00:54,550 --> 00:00:56,230
I don't know either

14
00:01:05,670 --> 00:01:08,550
Hey, those three handsome guys in the back

15
00:01:08,590 --> 00:01:11,910
Why is only one of them
in class today?

16
00:01:12,110 --> 00:01:14,430
I heard one of them
went to study in Japan

17
00:01:14,430 --> 00:01:17,230
And another one
went to Yale University

18
00:01:18,270 --> 00:01:23,470
Yale? That's impressive!
No wonder he's sitting there alone

19
00:01:23,830 --> 00:01:28,630
So lonely. Did the other two
really leave without saying goodbye?

20
00:01:28,630 --> 00:01:33,430
Yeah, probably not.
Haven't heard anything about it. Strange

21
00:01:35,110 --> 00:01:37,750
Poor guy.
He probably wasn't told goodbye

22
00:01:38,830 --> 00:01:41,750
All good things must come to an end

23
00:01:41,750 --> 00:01:45,630
Just like every relationship
comes quickly and goes quickly

24
00:01:45,630 --> 00:01:47,190
Like a gust of wind

25
00:02:21,590 --> 00:02:24,310
Let me go! Let go!

26
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:30,510
You've ruined my entire life

27
00:02:30,510 --> 00:02:32,550
The scars you've left me with

28
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:36,110
Can't be covered up with BB cream

29
00:02:37,890 --> 00:02:42,829
Even if I'm not pretty
I could still get plastic surgery

30
00:02:44,930 --> 00:02:50,750
But how am I supposed to heal
the wounds you left in my heart?

31
00:02:51,420 --> 00:02:53,200
-Bin, listen to me-
-I won't listen-

32
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:57,150
Bin, Bin, Bin

33
00:02:59,950 --> 00:03:01,000
Listen to me

34
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:09,090
Let me personally heal
the wounds in your heart

35
00:03:13,610 --> 00:03:18,370
Because I'm the one
who destroyed everything

36
00:03:23,329 --> 00:03:27,530
Let me take care of you
until your heart shines again

37
00:03:34,329 --> 00:03:35,610
Trust me

38
00:03:52,490 --> 00:03:54,290
Weren't you going to Yale?

39
00:03:59,010 --> 00:04:03,570
Yale what Yale?
I'd rather stay here and heal my love's heart

40
00:04:05,870 --> 00:04:08,710
[To be continued]
